  Own-tempo:

    This Pokémon cannot be confused.

  If a Pokémon is confused and 
  acquires this ability, its confusion 
  will immediately be healed.

  Stamina:

    Raises this Pokémon's Defense 
  by one stage when it takes damage 
  from a move.

  Inner-focus:

    This Pokémon cannot flinch.


